<img src="https://www.thehotelguru.com/_images/2f/c5/2fc52e0efd388b3586fc027f93dda871/s440x294.jpg" alt="The Mercer">
<br /><a href="/hotel/the-mercer-new-york" class="hotel-link">See more photos</a>
